<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="73" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1276,1555]" pageId="2" pageNumber="73">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,1493,1519]" pageId="2" pageNumber="73">Remarks:</emphasis>
So far, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rong &amp; Li" authorityYear="2017" box="[404,505,1492,1518]" class="Insecta" family="Pyralidae" genus="Locastra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="73" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridis">
<emphasis box="[404,505,1492,1518]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="73">L. viridis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been recorded from 
<collectingCountry box="[779,846,1492,1518]" name="China" pageId="2" pageNumber="73">China</collectingCountry>
(Xiajinchang). In the present study we report it from Dodak, 
<collectingRegion box="[240,324,1528,1554]" country="India" name="Sikkim" pageId="2" pageNumber="73">Sikkim</collectingRegion>
, which is the 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[477,613,1528,1555]" pageId="2" pageNumber="73">first record</emphasis>
of this species for 
<collectingCountry box="[825,886,1528,1554]" name="India" pageId="2" pageNumber="73">India</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
